a href="https://twitter.com/_kanade_kanon" target="_blank" rel="noopener">花出花音</a>、<a href="https://twitter.com/Uge_And" target="_blank" rel="noopener">安藤佑格</a>、 <a href="https://twitter.com/Cichan_dayo" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Ci-chan</a> ，而配音者春日部<a href="https://tsumugi-official.studio.site/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">紬</a>则基于 VTuber<a href="https://twitter.com/kasukaBe_nyoki" target="_blank" rel="noopener">春日部侑</a>的配音。它可以从新版本的 VX-β 中获得。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Nemurewatagashi / Hifumi feat. Hanasou Kanon β" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/CaeSu7L1XqY?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Retroid / Junky feat.Yuge Ando β" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/PVaWaIB5l0s?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>此外，作曲家创作的歌曲也将作为音库样本陆续发布。每个人都可以使用语音库和自己演唱的版本。 《Ci-chan β》和《Kasukabe Tsumugi β》预定于9月22日（星期五）发售。</p><p> （参考）<a href="https://vocaloid.beta.yamaha.com/news_007/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">新闻稿</a>、<a href="https://twitter.com/vocaloid_beta" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官方X（原Twitter）</a></p><p>帖子<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com/vocaloid-beta-studio-vtuber-voice-bank/">“Vocaloid β Studio”包括 VTuber Kanon Hanasode、Yuge Ando 和 Ci-chan Voiceroid Tsumugi Kasukabe 的声音，这些声音也</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.moguravr.com">Mogura VR</a>上。</p> ;
